Based on the above work, an undirected and edge-weighted network that changes dynamically over time is obtained. The next step is to extract the minimum spanning tree from the dynamic region network at each moment. In detail, when Italy is on the t day of the COVID-19 pandemic, we could extract the minimum spanning tree \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
